context:
KR:
&lt;뭐?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Huh?&gt;

KR:
&lt;콩콩이파?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Tingtang Gang?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…그래.&gt;
EN:
&lt;…Right.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…정말 저대로 내버려 두어도 괜찮은 걸까?&gt;
EN:
&lt;…Is it really okay to leave them be?&gt;

KR:
&lt;잠깐만… 그 단어는…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Wait… Not that word…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;누군가의 가치관과는… 크게… 동떨어지는… 발언인데…&gt;
EN:
&lt;That… does not align with a certain someone’s… beliefs…&gt;

KR:
&lt;안돼…! 돈키호테…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Oh no…! Don Quixote…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;그렇게 쳐다봐도 소용없어. 내 선에서 저 녀석의 통제는 불가능하단 말이야…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don’t give me that look. There’s nothing in my abilities to keep her under control…&gt;

KR:
&lt;아하, 그 말을 기억했는데도 튀어 나간 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Uh-huh. So you remembered his words and still leapt forward?&gt;

KR:
&lt;돈키호테…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don Quixote…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;일단…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Let’s just…&gt;

KR:
&lt;일단 밖으로 나가!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Let’s get outta here first!&gt;
